name: My workout app
body:
== README This is the repo for a workout tracker I built in the BDD with Ruby On Rails class.
Feel free to sign up, test the app in production and record your own workouts below: http://workout-lounge.herokuapp.com/ ![runners](http://us.cdn4.123rf.com/168nwm/grynold/grynold1109/grynold110900016/10459874-drawing-competition-on-run.jpg)
